<image 1> On the basis of style, this work can be attributed to

A. Paul Cézanne
B. Claude Monet
C. José María Velasco
D. Vincent van Gogh

The painting in the image is characterized by its swirling, expressive brushstrokes and dynamic sky, which are hallmarks of Vincent van Gogh's style. Therefore, the correct answer is:

D. Vincent van Gogh
